                      "text": "",
                      "raw_text": "<p class=\"hide-small\">In 2007, they became one of the first Colombian companies to export local fashion, paving the way for the hundreds that would follow in their footsteps.</p>\n<br>\nThanks to the unique handmade designs, Agua Bendita quickly developed into a leading brand in Colombia, with thirty stores nationwide. Today, the label is also present in over fifty countries worldwide.\n<br>\n<h3 style=\"color: #f57373; font-size:20px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:3.5px;margin-top:20px; margin-bottom:10px;\"> WHAT IS YOUR DESIGN PHILOSOPHY?</h3>\nAgua Bendita's design philosophy is teamwork. We believe in the power of teamwork in co-creating: our people, the soul of this company. We have been growing with our team over the years. This experience has been beautiful and challenging. What we admire the most is our team's transformation at Agua Bendita. We are all working for the same dream: the Agua Bendita dream!\n<br><br>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #f57373; font-size:20px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:3.5px;margin-top:20px; margin-bottom:10px;\"> WHAT MAKES YOUR <br>LABEL UNIQUE?</h3>\nWhat makes Agua Bendita unique are our ABhearts. You can see our uniqueness all over our handmade in-house illustrated prints and in our handcrafted details in every embroidered piece made by Colombian artisan women. We love that our ABhearts work in their homes as stay-home moms raising their children. They are definitely empowered women. All this makes our product even more special and unique.",
                      "hidden_br_mobile": false,
                      "hidden_on_desktop": false,
                      "hidden_on_mobile": true,
                      "text_align": "end",
                      "text_align_mb": "none",
                      "text_size": "custom",
