                      "text_color_link": "#c9a564",
                      "max_width": 0,
                      "font_family_type": "body",
                      "font_size_text_lg": 16,
                      "font_size_text_md": 14,
                      "font_size_text": 14,
                      "font_weight_text": 400,
                      "force_custom_size": false
                    },
                    "blocks": {}
                  },
                  "text_LRpEcN": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "name": "Text",
                    "settings": {
                      "text": "",
                      "raw_text": "<strong><h2 style=\"color: #000000; font-size:16px; \"> CATALINA ÁLVAREZ</h2></strong>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #f57373; font-size:20px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:2px;margin-top:20px; margin-bottom:20px;\"> WHAT CHARACTERISTICS SET <br>YOUR BRAND APART?</h3>\nColors! We mix all the Pantone colors perfectly. Combinations that make every single piece authentic... Our prints are handmade in-house, our artisans take more than a day doing a single drawing. Then, all of these drawings are digitalized and printed into fabrics with placed prints. Finally, our designs get into unique hands, the hands of our AB hearts. Then, they handcraft our pieces.\n<br><br>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #f57373; font-size:20px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:2px;margin-top:40px; margin-bottom:20px;\"> HOW DOES YOUR BRAND ENGAGE WITH LOCAL ARTISANS?</h3>\nABhearts were born with Agua Bendita. Colombian local artisan women that have been with us since day one. This is our favorite story, the one we are incredibly proud of. We used to do all of our designs from scratch. One day we realized we needed more hands. \n<br><br>In Colombia, we found artisans with the ability to make handmade embroideries, a learned task from past generations. We have helped all of these women create their own companies, working from home, raising their children, and at the same time, supporting their families!",
                      "hidden_br_mobile": false,
                      "hidden_on_desktop": true,
                      "hidden_on_mobile": false,
                      "text_align": "center",
