                      "text": "<p><em><strong>Meet The Designers Behind Agua by Agua Bendita</strong></em><br/><br/>Agua by Agua Bendita has become a favourite summer brand of the fashion elite. To find out what’s made it such a success, we sat down with its creative directors Mariana Hinestroza and Catalina Álvarez to talk inspiration, personal style and must-have pieces. How did you meet? <br/><br/>“We met while studying fashion design at university. We used to spend all our summers in Cartagena and one year, after a holiday with friends, we started making swimsuits using leftover fabrics from a local factory on my grandmother’s sewing machines...\"</p>",
