                    "name": "Text",
                    "settings": {
                      "text": "",
                      "raw_text": "<br>\nTRAVESÍA - \"We have traveled a path of memorable events.\" The story behind the story. \"Our luggage has been transformed at every destination. Each summer trip becomes the perfect expedition to collect nomadic objects, beautiful shapes, images, and stories that will always embody our creations.\" - Mariana Hinestroza and Catalina Álvarez, co-founders of Agua Bendita. Every drop of the collection tells a story that is represented by an element, as every object they have recollected in time becomes a unique creation, an AB collection: A Bouquet, a Chinese takeout box, a jaguar totem, a sketchbook, Egyptian tapestry, a Porto pottery vase, and a sunflower skirt that changed AB forever.\n<br>",
