                  "text_cdhxkb": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "name": "Text",
                    "settings": {
                      "text": "<p>For this season, Agua and Esvcdo lean into a harmonious space with unique handmade legacies to forge an extraordinary collaboration. United by a shared commitment to craftsmanship, weaving a tapestry of artistry and embracing Latin American heritage into every stitch. This collaboration features a venture into knitwear with the use of graceful fabrics, including Baby Alpaca and Wool, as well as never-before seen silhouettes in Agua including sweaters and coats, perfect for the windy weather.</p>",
