                  "text_kKgxYm": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "name": "Text",
                    "settings": {
                      "text": "",
                      "raw_text": "<p>We celebrate Colombia, its life, people, colors, flowers, diversity, wildlife, and joy for our daily inspiration. Agua Bendita pays tribute to the ancestral techniques with which the hands of our artisans transform our pieces into works of art. We remember who we are and what unites us between stitch and stitch—honoring the handmade through exclusive pieces embroidered by our #ABhearts since 2003. Each print is hand-illustrated and placed in perfect silhouettes by our in-house artists.</p>\n<br>\n<p>Agua Bendita is feminine, fun, colorful, vibrant, maximalist, sexy, eclectic, trendy, and handmade. “Playful and forever young.\"</p>",
