                  "text_bKpKJh": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "name": "Text",
                    "settings": {
                      "text": "<p><br/>This season Agua by Agua Bendita is thrilled to present Símbolo, a collection inspired by the marvelous world of sacred geometry. Blurring the limits between mother nature’s sublime forms, graphic design, and architectural motifs, such as mosaics, openworks, and coffers, this SS23, we’ve created exquisite garments in patterns that honor the charm of repetition and explore the infinite potential of elemental shapes. <br/><br/> As usual, breathtaking beadwork and rich embroideries promise to steal the spotlight. And, for the first time, we’ve introduced a unique monogram print that is bound to become an Agua classic. Featuring breezy pareos, sumptuous silk scarves, flattering swimsuits, and our beloved matching sets and ultra-feminine dresses in an array of lengths and novel silhouettes, Símbolo celebrates the ever-curious spirit of the Agua woman.</p>",
