                      "text": "<p><br/>This season, Agua by Agua Bendita is thrilled to present Marca, an ode to seaside nostalgia and saltwater gems. Evoking the allure of Colombia's varied coastal landscapes, and childhood memories by the sea, this unique collection spotlights hand-drawn motifs of precious seashells, stunning seaweed species in lieu of leaves, algae immortalized in cerulean cyanotypes, and nacre-inspired blooms that call to mind a beachside paradise. Per usual, exquisite fabrics with perfectly-placed prints and embellishments handsewn by brilliant artisans promise to be front and center.</p>",
