                    "name": "Text",
                    "settings": {
                      "text": "",
                      "raw_text": "This collection celebrates the nomadic spirit movement. Prints and silhouettes that travel from the past to meet the contemporary versions of imaginaries connected with the colorful, and vibrant spirit of Agua Bendita. To understand the value of a second in an ordinary day, to keep it in your heart as a memory: that makes us lucky. This collection is inspired by the power that recollections have when being written in our memory. Sometimes these memories arrive with the perfect dose of stillness. To understand the majesty of details, the small and invisible.",
