                  "text_PrrRJJ": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "name": "Text",
                    "settings": {
                      "text": "",
                      "raw_text": "<br>\nPacífico is the story of a nautical journey on a sailboat that travels along the Asian coast and the Pacific. A physical journey where memories and traditions are recovered at each stop. It is the memory of markets, crafts, sunsets, flavors, beaches, art, gardens, maps, architecture, flowers, feelings, love, and a grand final party.\n<br><br>\nThis collection is a diary that narrates different explorations at every stop, represented by each drop. It seeks to create a surreal story full of visual richness for this resort season.\n<br>",
