                      "text": "<p>Agua takes great pleasure in presenting an exquisite collection of garments designed for sophisticated layering, crafting versatile urban ensembles that effortlessly transition between the vibrancy of coastal cities and the dynamic energy of concrete jungles. From luxuriously snug turtle-neck bodysuits that seamlessly complement vibrant sweaters and opulent coats, to gracefully draped midi dresses that harmonize with knee-length boots; or the allure of an enchanting floral skirt paired with a casually elegant white boyfriend button-up. Immerse yourself in Marea’s resort glamour, where newfound day-to-day perspectives unfold against the backdrop of this editorial, captured amidst the blossoms of springtime Paris.</p>",
