                      "raw_text": "<p>In a winter’s embrace, a garden unfolds as a muse begins her Northern voyage. Inspired by her courageous journey, the collection reflects her resilient spirit, and the illustrations narrate the story of her quest, capturing the spirit of the frost-absorbed landscapes and her Colombian roots. \n<br><br>\nHorizontes, encapsulates the essence of an adventurer spirit by harmonizing the beauty found in the soil of the frosty ground and the blooms that emerge within her garden.</p>\n\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://us.aguabyaguabendita.com/collections/horizontes-collection\" title=\"Horizontes Collection\"><strong><u>SHOP THE COLLECTION</u></strong></a><br><br>",
