                  "text_w3rN99": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "name": "Text",
                    "settings": {
                      "text": "<p><br/>For the Resort 25 season, we are thrilled to present Aurora, an enthralling collection inspired by the odyssey of a soul in search of an eternal garden through the valleys of Colombia. Evoking the allure of Colombia’s rich flora and fauna, we present exquisite garments in soft pastel hues reminiscent of the season. The collection showcases exquisite 3D butterflies, specifically the mariposa blanca / lymanopoda paramera, an endemic species of Colombia, alongside beloved coffers, a signature of Agua since its very first collection. <br/><br/><br/><br/><a href=\"https://www.aguabyaguabendita.com/collections/aurora-collection\" title=\"Aurora  Collection\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em><strong>DISCOVER  AURORA</strong></em></span></a></p>",
