                      "text": "",
                      "raw_text": "<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0598/7831/0042/files/Logo-Olympics.png?v=1720851876\" alt=\"Athletic Club | Agua Bendita Capsule\" style=\"max-width: 300px; margin: 20px \nauto;\">\n<p>Unleash the spirit of victory and the uniqueness of Colombian design in our Athletic Club capsule. This collection, a tribute to the timeless strength and unity found in the world of sports.</p>\n<br><br>\n<p>Each piece in this collection celebrates the dynamic energy and determination of the <strong>Colombian athletes</strong>, reimagined through the lens of our signature artistry. With bold colors and intricate details, we invite you to champion your own triumphs and revel in the inspiring journey that lies ahead. Discover the capsule &amp; join us in commemorating the extraordinary beauty of the sport spirit.</p>",
