                      "text": "<p>This season, Agua by Agua Bendita presents Wild—a special capsule created in collaboration with Colombian artist Andrea Wild Botero. Inspired by her childhood across the Caribbean coast and countryside of Colombia, each piece is adorned with delicate, hand-drawn motifs that echo sunlit days, tropical fruit, and the timeless magic of home.<br/><br/>Botero brings to this collaboration a deeply personal vision—shaped by a life immersed in art, and reawakened by a return to painting. Her illustrations are paired with Agua’s signature coffers, a hallmark of our design language from the very beginning, creating a dialogue between past and present, artist and artisan.<br/><br/><br/><a href=\"/collections/andrea-wild-collection\" title=\"Andrea Wild Collection\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em><strong>SHOP NOW</strong></em></span></a></p>",
                      "raw_text": "",
                      "hidden_br_mobile": false,
                      "hidden_on_desktop": false,
