                  "text_mim7bB": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "name": "Text",
                    "settings": {
                      "text": "<p>Zacapa x Agua by AB arrives as a curated collection of bespoke offerings gathered into one illustrious set. Each piece uniquely captures the spirit of the lands and people that made it. First, a bottle of Zacapa XO, aged above the clouds in the Guatemalan highlands for an inimitably smooth medley of mature and lifting flavors like dark cherry and clove. Accompanying the rum are an elaborately shaped wooden spoon and a pair of delicate hand-painted ceramic glasses—perfect for an intimate toast with a friend or a sumptuous nightcap.</p>",
