                  "text_kcBiGQ": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "name": "Text",
                    "settings": {
                      "text": "<p>This season Agua by Agua Bendita is thrilled to present Secreto, a collection inspired by the untouched and secret natural havens of Latin America. The collection embraces the spirits of these sacred places through designs that echo precision and heritage, immortalizing the region’s endemic flora and fauna. With exquisite embroidery and hand-illustrated details, these pieces portray the beauty of the blooms and wildlife with extraordinary homage.<br/><br/>The art of scientific illustrations becomes our signature for the High Summer / Fall Winter season, celebrating the craftsmanship and storytelling of a former era.With flowy, fresh silhouettes and versatile dresses that transition easily from day-to-night, this season's pieces reflect the timeless beauty of our land. Step into a world where the past meets the present and we uncover the world’s most best-kept secrets.</p>",
