                  "text_EDdi3M": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "name": "Text",
                    "settings": {
                      "text": "<p>This season, we are proud to present an exclusive capsule with the renowned Colombian artist, Andrea Wild Botero, who has a deep artistic heritage in her roots. The capsule named “Wild” features delicate hand-illustrated motifs that resemble her childhood memories in Cartagena, combined with coffers, an Agua signature element that has been in our designs from the very beginning. Each piece is a reflection of our commitment to exhibit the unexplored beauty of our region. For this special edition, we asked Andrea some questions regarding her inspiration and her roots.</p>",
