                  "text_xHB6TT": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "name": "Text",
                    "settings": {
                      "text": "<p>My love of art was instilled in me from the day I was born by my parents and grandparents. Art runs through my veins. It's what I've known, loved and been surrounded by since I can remember. It's not only that they loved to take me to museums and galleries but they've always been passionate about art history and ever-curious about the ins and outs of the art market. To this day, art is one of the main subjects at the dinner table.</p>",
