                    "blocks": {
                      "block_tabs_html_B3qPpM": {
                        "type": "_block-tabs-html",
                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "How can I know my size?",
                          "content": "<p>You can check our size guide <a href=\"https://www.aguabendita.com/pages/size-guide\" title=\"Size Guide | Agua Bendita USA\"><em>here</em></a>. Also, if you have any questions don’t hesitate to contact us at <a href=\"mailto:customercare@aguabendita.com.co\" target=\"_blank\"><em>customercare@aguabendita.com.co</em></a>, and we will be more than happy to assist you.</p>",
                          "page": ""
                        },
                        "blocks": {}
                      },
                      "block_tabs_html_abLcbk": {
                        "type": "_block-tabs-html",
                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "How do I track my order?",
                          "content": "<p>You will receive an email with the tracking information within 1 business day after your purchase.</p>",
                          "page": ""
                        },
                        "blocks": {}
                      },
                      "block_tabs_html_Y8TaUA": {
                        "type": "_block-tabs-html",
                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "When will I receive my order?",
                          "content": "<p>• Orders placed Monday to Friday before 12 pm EST are shipped the same day. Orders placed after 12 pm EST or on Saturdays, Sundays, or Holidays are shipped the next <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">business</span> day. </p><p>• ETA is 1-9 business days depending on the State. You can see accurate times at the checkout after entering your address.</p><p>• We ship with UPS, USPS, and FedEx. Orders destined to PO Boxes, APO Boxes, or military addresses will be shipped only with USPS, and transit time may take longer.</p>",
                          "page": ""
                        },
                        "blocks": {}
                      },
                      "block_tabs_html_dBNc7P": {
                        "type": "_block-tabs-html",
                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "Do you have expedited shipping?",
                          "content": "<p>• Yes, we offer an Express 2-day service and a Next-day service at the checkout. The price depends on the state. You can see accurate fees at the checkout.</p><p>• This service can not be requested or paid after the order is placed.</p><p>• Orders placed Monday to Friday before 12 pm EST are shipped the same day. Orders placed after 12 pm EST or on Saturdays, Sundays, or Holidays are shipped the next <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">business</span> day. </p>",
                          "page": ""
                        },
                        "blocks": {}
                      },
                      "block_tabs_html_ggXn8a": {
                        "type": "_block-tabs-html",
                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "Where do you ship from?",
                          "content": "<p>Our warehouse is located in Miami, Florida.</p>",
                          "page": ""
                        },
                        "blocks": {}
                      },
                      "block_tabs_html_fjHMXR": {
                        "type": "_block-tabs-html",
                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "Can I cancel or modify my order prior to shipping?",
                          "content": "<p>Unfortunately, we are unable to process order modifications regarding items and sizes. To request an address change or a complete order cancellation please contact us as soon as possible by filling out <a href=\"https://www.aguabendita.com/pages/customer-service-contact-form\" title=\"Customer Service Contact Form | Agua Bendita USA\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>this form</em></span></a> by email at <a href=\"mailto:customercare@aguabendita.com.co\" title=\"Customer Contact Email | Agua Bendita\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>customercare@aguabendita.com</em></span></a> and provide the complete and detailed new address. Please take into account that <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">this request must be placed from the same email address that issued the purchase.</span></p><p>Our Customer Care team will do everything possible to correct the delivery address and keep you posted about it. However, <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">this will always depend on the order status</span>, and Agua Bendita cannot guarantee the change will be successfully applied.</p><p>In 1-2 business days, our customer care team will confirm, depending on the order status, if it was possible to successfully complete your request.</p>",
                          "page": ""
                        },
                        "blocks": {}
                      },
                      "block_tabs_html_49aRDK": {
                        "type": "_block-tabs-html",
                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "Can I return my order?",
                          "content": "<p>We have a 30-days return policy. Items must be unworn and returned in the original package. For more information, please click <a href=\"https://www.aguabendita.com/pages/return-and-exchange\" title=\"Shipping and Returns | Agua Bendita USA\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>here</em></span></a>.</p>",
                          "page": ""
                        },
                        "blocks": {}
                      },
                      "block_tabs_html_7PwH99": {
                        "type": "_block-tabs-html",
                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "When will I receive my refund?",
                          "content": "<p>Your refund will be issued to your original payment method, and it can take 10-15 business days <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">after your return package arrives</span> at our warehouse. You will receive an email confirmation once your refund is processed. Shipping fees (both standard and express) are non-refundable.</p>",
                          "page": ""
                        },
                        "blocks": {}
                      },
                      "block_tabs_html_dTAaBK": {
                        "type": "_block-tabs-html",
                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "What are our customer service hours?",
                          "content": "<p>Our customer care team is available: </p><ul><li>Monday to Thursday: 8 AM to 6 PM (Colombian time) except local holidays.</li><li>Friday: 8 AM to 5 PM (Colombian time) except local holidays.</li></ul><p>Your requests might take up to 1 business day to be attended.</p>",
                          "page": ""
                        },
                        "blocks": {}
                      }
