                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "TERMS OF USE",
                          "content": "<p>Everything described in this section applies exclusively to visitors of <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">www.aguabendita.com</span> and purchases made on this website.</p><h3>CONSENT</h3><p>Welcome! We appreciate your interest in Agua Bendita. We invite you to review our website’s terms and conditions, and if you have any disputes regarding them, please proceed to leave the website as soon as possible.<br/><br/>By visiting www.aguabendita.com and/or purchasing something, you agree and consent to these Terms & Conditions (Terms of service), along with our personal data treatment (Privacy Policy), which includes the general terms on how the transactions are made once there is a purchase through this website. <br/><br/>Any customer under the age of 18 must inform their parents or legal guardians. Every registry and usage inside the website must be done by a representative agreeing to the legal regime and shall share his opinion before giving authorization on managing or giving any sort of personal information. <br/><br/>By using this site, you represent that you are at least the age of majority in your state or province of residence, or that your parents or legal guardians and you have given us your consent to allow any of your minor dependents to use this site.<br/><br/>We invite you to review our terms and conditions, and if you have any dispute regarding them, please proceed to leave the website as soon as possible.</p><h3>INTRODUCTION</h3><p>For effects of the information contained in these Terms and Conditions, hereinafter the terms “platform” and “website” shall be understood as www.aguabendita.com; “The User” shall be understood as any person who enters and navigates www.aguabendita.com, purchase any items or create an account and a password by their own means and “Agua Bendita” a reference to Agua Bendita SAS.<br/><br/>The regulation applicable to these Terms and Conditions is the United States law, being this platform mainly addressed to residents located within the American territory.<br/><br/>Agua Bendita reserves the right at any time to modify or discontinue this platform service and shall not be liable to the user or to any third-party for any modification, price change, suspension, or discontinuance of the Service.</p><h3>MODIFICATION AND UPDATE OF TERMS AND CONDITIONS</h3><p>These terms and conditions are subject to change without previous notification and shall be applicable from the moment of its publication on our website. Agua Bendita reserves the right, at our sole discretion, to update, change, or replace any part of these Terms and conditions.<br/><br/>Consequently, it is the User's responsibility to check and read the platform’s “Terms and conditions” (this page) and “Privacy Policy” <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>(</em></span><a href=\"https://www.aguabendita.com/pages/privacy-policy\" title=\"Privacy Policy | Agua Bendita USA\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>click here</em></span></a><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>)</em></span> every time the User either visits or makes a transaction on the platform.<br/><br/>The user’s continued use or access to this website and services following the posting of any changes to these Terms and Conditions constitutes acceptance of those changes.</p><h3>ERRORS, INACCURACIES, AND OMISSIONS</h3><p>Occasionally there may be information on the platform that contains typographical errors, inaccuracies, or omissions that may relate to product descriptions, pricing, promotions, offers, product shipping charges, transit times, and availability. Agua Bendita reserves the right to correct any errors, inaccuracies or omissions by mistake, and to change or update information if it is inaccurate, at any time and without prior notice (including after an order has been submitted).<br/>Agua Bendita undertakes no obligation to update, amend, or clarify information in the platform service or on any related website, including, without any limitation, pricing information, except as required by law. No specified update or refresh date applied in the Service or on any related website, should be taken to indicate that all information in the Service or on any related website has been modified or updated.</p><h3>INDEMNIFICATION</h3><p>The User agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless Agua Bendita and any subsidiaries, affiliates, partners, officers, directors, agents, contractors, licensors, service providers, subcontractors, suppliers, interns, and employees, harmless from any claim or demand, including reasonable attorneys’ fees, made by any third-party due to or arising out of the User breach of these Terms and conditions or the documents they incorporate by reference or the User violation of any law or the rights of a third-party.</p><h3>SEVERABILITY</h3><p>If any provision of these Terms and Conditions is determined to be unlawful, void, or unenforceable, such provision shall nonetheless be enforceable to the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, and the unenforceable portion shall be deemed to be severed from these Terms and conditions, such determination shall not affect the validity and enforceability of any other remaining provisions.</p><h3>DISCLOSURE</h3><p>Agua Bendita may disclose your personal information if it is required by law to do so or if the User has violated these Terms and Conditions.<br/><br/>The User acknowledges and agrees that Agua Bendita may preserve the User's access and inquiry information, and use that information if required by law or in a good faith belief that preservation, use, or disclosure of such access and inquiry information is reasonably necessary to (a) comply with a legal process; (b) enforce this User Agreement, (c) respond to claims that any Materials violate the rights of third parties; (d) respond to requests for service; or (e) protect the rights, property or personal safety of Agua Bendita, its users and the public.</p><h3>PERSONAL INFORMATION</h3><p>The User submission of personal information through this platform is governed by our Privacy Policy. To view The User's rights under the California Consumer Privacy Act, and our Privacy Policy, <a href=\"https://www.aguabendita.com/pages/privacy-policy\" title=\"Privacy Policy | Agua Bendita USA\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>click here</em></span></a>. </p><h3>CONTACT INFORMATION</h3><p>For effects of the platform usage, personal information, purchasing, or any kind of request intended directly to Agua Bendita SAS, the User can reach out to the following:<br/><br/>• Email: <a href=\"mailto:customercare@aguabendita.com.co\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Email Customer Contact | Agua Bendita\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>customercare@aguabendita.com.co</em></span></a></p><p> </p><p>• Whats App: <a href=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=573146277470\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"What's App Customer Contact | Agua Bendita\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>+57 314 627 7470</em></span></a></p><p> </p><p>• Address: 5220 NW 72nd Ave #3 - Miami, Florida 33166 USA</p>",
