                      "block_tabs_html_dBNc7P": {
                        "type": "_block-tabs-html",
                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "PRODUCTS AND SERVICES",
                          "content": "<p>Everything described in this section applies exclusively to visitors of <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">www.aguabendita.com</span> and purchases made on this website.</p><h3><strong>AVAILABILITY</strong></h3><p>Certain products or services may be available exclusively online through the website. Agua Bendita reserves the right to limit the quantities of any offered products or services and to discontinue any product at any time. All product descriptions and pricing are subject to change at any time without notice.<br/><br/>Agua Bendita reserves the right but is not obligated, to limit the sales of our products or Services to any person, geographic region, or jurisdiction. This may be exercised on a case-by-case basis.<br/><br/>Agua Bendita only warrants the quality of any products, services, information, or other material that is purchased or obtained on this platform.</p><h3><strong>COLORS</strong></h3><p>Agua Bendita has done everything to show to the User the most reliable and precise colors on the products. Nonetheless, these may differ depending on which screen or device the User is viewing the platform’s products. Some small color variations or other types of minor variations may occur on the offered products, resulting from the different image and display acquisition technologies or from other technical reasons. Agua Bendita does not take any responsibility for such variations and deviations.</p><h3><strong>PRICES, OFFERS, AND DISCOUNTS*</strong></h3><p>Agua Bendita reserves the right to determine the price of the products and make changes to them without prior notice. Still, the amount applicable to the User's order will be the published price at the checkout. Once the User makes the payment, the order is accepted.<br/><br/>Prices are expressed in USD, and sales taxes are not included in the price expressed within the platform information. Agua Bendita reserves the right to make changes to prices and products before any order is placed by The User. Once The User has placed an order, Agua Bendita shall be bound to keep the purchase conditions set forth at the time the purchase was made on the platform. Agua Bendita reserves the right to change, limit, or terminate special offers at any time.<br/><br/>Agua Bendita does not offer a price adjustment on purchased items whose price has been temporarily reduced after the transaction was made. Once an item has been purchased on Sale with or without a discount code, there will be no changes in its price or refunds of the difference between the price paid and the new price that would have been published after the order's payment.<br/><br/>Agua Bendita charges shipping expenses that vary depending on the destination state or country. The shipping fee is expressed in the purchase summary (checkout) at the time of acquiring the product. Such shipping expenses shall be invoiced, when required, on an independent basis and shall be specified and added up to the total price of the order.<br/><br/>Discounts with promotional or seasonal coupons are not cumulative among them or any products with a discount already applied at the online store.<br/><br/><strong>Products under “Final Sale” identifications cannot be returned, refunded, or exchanged. Discounts with promotional or seasonal coupons are not cumulative among them or any products with a discount already applied at the online store</strong></p><h3><strong>SALES TAX</strong></h3><p>State and local sales tax rates and applications are determined by the destination where the products are being shipped. Taxes will be applied during the checkout and will be charged to The User's payment method.<br/><br/>These terms displayed are subject to change, as the taxation of online transactions is continually evolving. Agua Bendita strives to comply with state and local tax laws as they exist currently and continues to monitor and update its taxation policies as those laws change.<br/><br/>Orders shipped to Florida, Georgia, Illinois, New Jersey, North Carolina, Puerto Rico, and Texas, will have all applicable local and state sales taxes added to the total order amount, and to shipping charges when appropriate.</p><h3><strong>PRODUCT OWNERSHIP / PROPERTY</strong></h3><p>Products provided shall remain the exclusive property of Agua Bendita until the User has completely paid all the charges due in virtue of any remote purchase-sale agreement subscribed with us, including payment of shipping costs and all other expenses associated with the online purchase-sale agreement.<br/><br/>The purchased products will be the User’s property once the order is physically delivered to the User’s address provided in the purchase.<br/><br/>In case the User provides a wrong delivery address, Agua Bendita is not responsible for orders that get lost due to the customer's providing an incorrect shipping address. If the mistake is reported on time, Agua Bendita will make everything possible to re-route the order to the correct address, which depends entirely on the carrier (DHL). Agua Bendita will not be held liable if this isn't possible or the package ends up being delivered to the original address provided by The User.</p>",
                          "page": ""
                        },
                        "blocks": {}
                      },
                      "block_tabs_html_P6Jf6G": {
                        "type": "_block-tabs-html",
                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "PAYMENT, PURCHASING AND ORDER HANDLING",
                          "content": "<p>Everything described in this section applies exclusively to visitors of <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">www.aguabendita.com</span> and purchases made on this website.</p><h3><strong>PAYMENT METHODS</strong></h3><p>Agua Bendita offers the following payment methods:<br/> • American Express<br/>• MasterCard<br/>• Visa<br/>• Discover Network (including Diner's Club)<br/>• PayPal<br/>• Sezzle: Buy now, Pay later. See how it works <a href=\"https://www.aguabendita.com/pages/sezzle\" title=\"Buy now, Pay later with Sezzle\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>here</em></span></a><br/> • Shop Pay (only applicable when previously set up in the Browser)<br/>• Apple Pay (only applicable when previously set up in the Browser)<br/>• Google Pay (only applicable when previously set up in the Browser)<br/>• Meta Pay (only applicable when previously set up in the Browser)<br/><br/><br/>Credit/Debit card payments are operated through Shopify Payments. It should be expressed that The User, at the time of paying the purchase through a credit card, uses and accepts Shopify Payment's terms of service which can be found <a href=\"https://www.shopify.com/legal/terms-payments/us\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shopify Payments | Terms of Service\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>here</em></span></a>. Agua Bendita does not accept checks, cash, money orders, or COD as payment.<br/><br/>When The User purchases through Sezzle, PayPal, or Shop Pay, after presenting the purchase summary during the sale process, shall leave Agua Bendita's platform for a short time period, and then access it again when The User gets to know the payment status (rejected or approved). The customer should register on the Sezzle / PayPal / Shop Pay platform, and once registered, the customer should be able to make a purchase. During this entire period, the applicable terms and conditions to the payment transaction (personal data for processing the payment, such as the credit card number, among others) that shall govern are the ones from the third-party payment platform, which can be validated directly on their websites: <br/><br/></p><p>• Shop Pay: <a href=\"https://shop.app/terms-of-service\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shop Pay terms and conditions\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>shop.app/terms-of-service</em></span></a></p><p>• Sezzle: <a href=\"https://legal.sezzle.com/user\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sezzle terms of use\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>legal.sezzle.com/user</em></span></a></p><p>• PayPal: <a href=\"https://www.paypal.com/co/webapps/mpp/ua/useragreement-full\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"PayPal terms of use\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>paypal.com/co/webapps/mpp/ua/useragreement-full</em></span></a></p><p><br/>After the payment is completed, the customer will be redirected again to www.aguabendita.com and the order will be confirmed.</p><h3><strong>LEGALIZATION OF ORDERS</strong></h3><p>Once the payment has been confirmed, Agua Bendita shall send the User an email confirming the detailed information of the purchase and the order number. This email represents the order has been legalized, received, and that it is soon to be processed. The User shall later receive a notification email updating the order status and the shipping tracking number.<br/><br/>By completing the payment and purchase, the User accepts the product’s paid price. Agua Bendita will not be responsible for discount/coupon codes not applied by the User when placing the order. Once the purchase has been legalized, Agua Bendita will not modify the purchase amount/paid price nor later apply coupon/discount codes.</p><h3><strong>SHIPPING AND DELIVERIES</strong></h3><p>To see all the information related to shipping, deliveries, order modifications, and order cancellatons, please check the full policy <a href=\"https://www.aguabendita.com/pages/shipping-and-delivery\" title=\"Shipping and Deliveries Policy | Agua Bendita USA\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>here</em></span></a>.</p><h3><strong>WARRANTIES AND RETURNS</strong></h3><p>To see all the information related to returns, exchanges, warranties, incomplete/incorrect orders, or refunds, please check the full policy <a href=\"https://www.aguabendita.com/pages/return-and-exchange\" title=\"Warranties, Returns, and Refunds Policy | Agua Bendita USA\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>here</em></span></a>.</p>",
                          "page": ""
                        },
                        "blocks": {}
                      },
                      "block_tabs_html_eFbDQx": {
                        "type": "_block-tabs-html",
                        "name": "Custom HTML",
                        "settings": {
                          "title": "CURRENT OFFERS AND PROMOTIONS",
                          "content": "<p>Everything described in this section applies exclusively to visitors of <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">www.aguabendita.com</span> and purchases made on this website.</p><h3><strong>CURRENT ONLINE OFFERS AND PROMOTIONS</strong></h3><p>None of the current offers are combinable with other discounts, promotions, Sale events, or any other offer. The value of the offers can never be redeemable for cash and cannot be applied to previous purchases.<br/><br/><strong>• Sale:</strong> up to 60% discount on selected references. Agua Bendita makes available to its customers a promotional incentive called \"Sale\" available in the online store www.aguabendita.com . The garments that qualify for the benefit will be found only under the \"SALE\" category (www.aguabendita.com/collections/sale). The discount is already applied to the price of each garment. Availability will be indicated in each product by selecting the size and including it in the cart. This incentive can't be accumulated with other discounts or promotions. Expenses and costs associated with the purchase, such as taxes, deductions, and withholdings, will be covered by the customer, and this will be informed at the checkout. In the case of warranties, the value paid for the garment will be recognized. Not combinable with other discounts or promotions in store. All items in this category and/or marked as \"Final Sale\" are not available for returns, exchanges, or refunds.<br/><br/><strong>• Subscription:</strong> for having filled out our Newsletter form, receive a 15% discount on your next purchase. Code available for single use only. Offer valid for 30 days from the moment you receive the email with the code, for your next purchase in the online store (www.aguabendita.com). Only one code is allowed per client. The discount is not redeemable for cash, and it does not apply to previous purchases. It can be combined with other offers or discounts. Exclusive for new clients.<br/><br/><strong>• Birthday discount:</strong> January 1 to 31, 2026: enjoy an exclusive 25% birthday discount for customers registered in the Agua Bendita database. Valid only during your birthday month with prior registration. To redeem, enter the code sent in the birthday email at the USA Online Store: https://aguabendita.com/collections/new. This offer cannot be combined with other discounts or promotions and is not redeemable for cash. It does not apply to special collaborations and/or limited launches. For online redemption, customers will need to enter the code they received via email or text message at the time of checkout. Valid for one (1) redemption during the birthday month. Promotional items are non-exchangeable, except in cases of warranty. For exchanges to a different item, the discount will not be retained; only the amount paid by the customer will be recognized. If the new item is of a lower value, the customer must add another item to complete the original amount or pay the difference if applicable.<br/><br/><strong>•AGUA BENDITA S.A.S. offers its customers the gift “PAREO.”</strong> This promotion will be valid from December 17 to 31, 2025, and/or while supplies last, whichever occurs first. The gift consists of a PAREO, subject to availability, with a total inventory of thirty (30) units, and will be granted to customers who visit the Aguabendita USA online store and make purchases over USD 250 in full-price products.To receive the gift, customers must manually add the pareo to their cart during the checkout process. The pareo will not be added automatically to the order. Orders that meet the minimum purchase requirement but do not include the pareo added manually at checkout will not be eligible for the gift.The pareo will be selected and delivered at random during order preparation and cannot be exchanged, substituted for any other item, or refunded in cash.<br/><br/><strong> </strong><br/><br/><strong>• EXTRA10 + FREE SHIPPING:</strong> AGUA BENDITA LLC presents the promotional activity titled “Additional 10% Off.” This promotion will be valid from From December 5 to 8, 2025, and applies to purchases made in the USA online store at https://aguabendita.com/collections/sale . The benefit will range from 30% to 60% off. The applicable collections and discounts are as follows: Resort 24, Summer 23, and previous collections: 80%; Black Sale Items 23, Solid Sale Items 24, and Tropic of C: 80%; Streetwear 24 and January Sale 25 Sale Items: 70%; Summer Sale July 24 Sale Items: 80%; Summer 24 (all groups): 70%; Black Sale Items 2024: 70%; Resort 25: 60%; Summer Sale July 2025 Sale Items: 60%; Summer 2025: 40%; Cherry Concept Store: 30%; Van Leuwenn: 40% (online only); and Black Sale Items 2025: 40%. During the event dates, an additional 10% will be applied to the current discount; that is, items with a 30% discount will increase to 40%, those with 40% will increase to 50%, and so on, until reaching the final discount percentage. The participating items will be grouped, and their availability will depend on each store’s inventory. Terms and Conditions: For online purchases, product availability will be displayed through size selection and confirmed once added to the cart. All shipping costs, taxes, deductions, and withholdings are covered by the customer and will be detailed at checkout along with the available payment methods.. Discounts will be automatically applied at checkout after the invoice is processed. This promotion cannot be combined with other discounts or promotions. Exchanges are not allowed. In the case of warranties, the amount paid for the item will be honored. Refunds will not be issued. Final sale items are non-returnable and non-exchangeable, as stated in our return policy (https://www.aguabendita.com/pages/shipping-and-returns). <br/><br/><strong>• Care Survey:</strong> 15% discount for customers who respond to the Customer Care Survey. Exclusively for selected clients who receive communication from the brand. This promotion can't be combined with other offers, discounts, or the Sale section. This discount is not redeemable for cash and must be used in one (1) single purchase. Valid for 1 single redemption per client. The bonus will be linked to the email of the selected person, and it is non-transferable.<br/><br/><strong>• Free Shipping on all orders:</strong> Agua Bendita makes available to its customers a promotional incentive called \"Free Shipping on all orders\" available in the online store www.aguabendita.com from November 26th, 2025, until November 27th, 2025. All purchases made in the online store are eligible for free standard shipping. No minimum amount is required. Applicable to all orders, full-price items, and sale items. The free shipping will be reflected at checkout for all standard options, including the PO BOX Standard option. Expedited shipping options such as \"Next Day: 1 business day\" or \"Express: 2 business days\" are not part of this promotional incentive; therefore, not free.<br/><br/><strong>• Sitewide 40% off:</strong> Promotion valid only at www.aguabendita.com . All available items on the website are discounted 40% off up to 80% off. The discount is already applied to the published price. Offer valid from October 18th at 7:00 PM CST, until October 20th at 8:00 AM CST, 2025. This promotion can't be combined with other offers, discounts. This discount is not redeemable for cash.<br/><br/><strong>• Buy 2 full-price and get 20% off:</strong> Promotion valid only at www.aguabendita.com . Add 2 or more items to the bag, and get a 20% discount on all items. The discount will automatically be applied to all full-price items. Promotion applicable only to full-price items. Offer valid on orders placed from October 7th at 12:00 PM CST, until October 14th at 8:00 AM CST, 2025. This promotion can't be combined with other offers, discounts, or the Sale section. This discount is not redeemable for cash.<br/><br/><strong>• Buy +3 full-price and get 25% off:</strong> Promotion valid only at www.aguabendita.com . Add 3 or more items to the bag, and get a 25% discount on all items. The discount will automatically be applied to all full-price items. Promotion applicable only to full-price items. Offer valid on orders placed from October 7th at 12:00 PM CST, until October 14th at 8:00 AM CST, 2025. This promotion can't be combined with other offers, discounts, or the Sale section. This discount is not redeemable for cash.<br/><br/><strong>• Get 15% off on pareos:</strong> Promotion valid only at www.aguabendita.com for selected customers who will receive the communication via email. The incentive is a 15% discount on pareos when applying the code at checkout. Offer valid until October 31st, 2025. This promotion can't be combined with other offers, discounts, or the Sale section. This discount is not redeemable for cash and must be used in one (1) single purchase. Valid for 1 single redemption per client.<br/><br/><strong>• Buy +3 and get one item with 20% off:</strong> Promotion valid only at www.aguabendita.com for selected customers who receive the communication via email with the code. Add 3 or more items to the bag, enter the code at checkout, and get one item with 20% off. The discount will be applied to the item with the lowest price. Promotion applicable only to full-price items and valid only when applying the code at checkout. Offer valid until October 31st. This promotion can't be combined with other offers, discounts, or the Sale section. This discount is not redeemable for cash and must be used in one (1) single purchase. Valid for 1 single redemption per client. <br/><br/><strong>• Agua Bendita x Soho:</strong> apply the code at checkout to receive 25% off on all full-price items. The discount will only be applied if the code is entered during checkout and will not be honored after the order is placed. This offer cannot be combined with any other promotion or discount. This promotion is valid only for customers who receive the code at the event and applies exclusively to purchases made on our US online store (www.aguabendita.com) from July 6th, 2025, through July 31st, 2025. 2025.<br/><br/><strong>• Bikini Days: 30% off on all women's and girls' swimwear:</strong> From July 5th at 9 AM, 2025 until July 7th, 2025 at 8 AM, 30% OFF on all one-piece swimsuits, bikini tops, and bikini bottoms available at www.aguabendita.com . The discount is already applied to the price of each garment. Availability will be indicated in each product by selecting the size and including it in the cart. This incentive can't be accumulated with other discounts or promotions. Expenses and costs associated with the purchase, such as taxes, deductions, and withholdings, will be covered by the customer, and this will be informed at the checkout. In the case of warranties, the value paid for the garment will be recognized. Not combinable with other discounts or promotions in store. All items on Sale are considered and tagged as \"Final Sale\". All items purchased during this event are not available for returns, exchanges, or refunds.<br/><br/><strong>• 4th of July Sale: 35% off sitewide:</strong> All the products available in the store www.aguabendita.com from July 3rd at 8 PM, 2025 until July 5th, 2025 at 8 AM, are applicable to this promotion. The discount is already applied to the price of each garment. Availability will be indicated in each product by selecting the size and including it in the cart. This incentive can't be accumulated with other discounts or promotions. Expenses and costs associated with the purchase, such as taxes, deductions, and withholdings, will be covered by the customer, and this will be informed at the checkout. In the case of warranties, the value paid for the garment will be recognized. Not combinable with other discounts or promotions in store. All items on Sale are considered and tagged as \"Final Sale\". All items purchased during this event are not available for returns, exchanges, or refunds.<br/><br/><strong>• Free Bandana on orders over $230:</strong> Applies only to full-price items in our USA Online store (www.aguabendita.com). One (1) bandana will be given to the customer for free on orders equal to or greater than $230 USD on full-price items. The price of the items on SALE doesn't add to the amount for this promotion. The bandana will be automatically included at checkout, and it does not apply to any kind of exchange or refund. This promotion is not cumulative with other discount codes or promotions described on this page. There are 76 bandana gifts available. This promotion is valid from June 13th, 2025 at 11:00 AM EST, until supplies last. In the event of returns, the customer must keep at least $230 USD in product. Otherwise, the bandana gift must be returned too. If the bandana is not returned, the refund will not be issued or the item's price (50 USD) will be deducted from the refund if the amount can be completely covered.<br/><br/><strong>• Bridal Season Giveaway:</strong> Agua Bendita presents the “GIVEAWAY USA BRIDAL SEASON”, a collaboration with Le Mini Macaron and Brinker + Eliza, running from March 11th to March 22nd, 2025, and exclusively available for participants in the United States. To enter, the bride must register along with her friends through the form that will be published on our Instagram, shared via official partner channels, and sent via email. The prize includes 6 swimsuits selected by Agua Bendita, 6 necklaces from Brinker + Eliza and Nail polishes from Le Mini Macaron, chosen by the brand. There will be one winner, who will be randomly selected along with her registered group of friends. The winner will be announced on March 22nd, 2025. Stay alert for fake accounts. We will never ask for personal information from any account other than @aguabenditasw @leminimacarron or @brinkerandeliza. This giveaway is not affiliated with Instagram. <br/><br/><strong>• Free Pareo on orders over $300:</strong> Applies only to full-price items in our USA Online store (www.aguabendita.com). One (1) pareo will be given to the customer for free on orders equal to or greater than $300 USD on full-price items. The price of the items on SALE doesn't add to the amount for this promotion. The pareo will be automatically included at checkout, and it does not apply to any kind of exchange or refund. This promotion is not cumulative with other discount codes or promotions described on this page. There are 75 pareo gifts available. This promotion is valid from February 28th, 2025 at 7:00 PM EST, until supply lasts. In the event of returns, the customer must keep at least $300 USD in product. Otherwise the pareo gift must be returned too. If the pareo is not returned, the refund will not be issued or the item's price (140 USD) will be deducted from the refund if the amount can be completely covered.<br/><br/><strong>• President's Day SALE - Extra 10% off on SALE:</strong> applies only to purchases in our US online store (www.aguabendita.com). Apply the code EXTRA10 at the checkout and get an extra 10% off on the “Sale” section. If the customer does not apply the code at the checkout, the discount will not be recognized after placing the order. This promotion is valid from February 14th, 2025 at 6:00 PM EST, until February 18th, 2025 at 7 AM EST. <br/><br/><strong>• Bucket Hat Gift:</strong> applies only to purchases in our US Online store (www.aguabendita.com). One (1) bucket hat will be given to the customer for free on orders equal to, or greater than $220 USD on full-price items. The pareo will be automatically included at checkout, and it does not apply to any kind of exchange. This promotion is valid from October 23rd, 2024 until supplies last. This promotion is not valid for purchases on discounted products (Sale).<br/><br/><strong>• Free Shipping on all orders:</strong> applies only to purchases in our US online store (www.aguabendita.com). Free Shipping on all orders is automatically included at checkout. Valid only for Standard-Shipping services. \"Express Shipping\" and \"Next-day\" Shipping services are not included in this promotion, therefore not free. This promotion is valid from 11:00 am EST on February 1st, 2025 until 7:00 am EST on February 5th, 2025.<br/><br/><strong>• End-of-Season SALE - Extra 10% off on SALE:</strong> applies only to purchases in our US online store (www.aguabendita.com). Apply the code EXTRA10 at the checkout and get an extra 10% off on the “Sale” section. If the customer does not apply the code at the checkout, the discount will not be recognized after placing the order. This promotion is valid only during the following time frames: -From 9:00 pm EST January 31st, 2025 until 9:00 am EST on February 1st, 2025. -From 9:00 pm EST February 1st, 2025 until 9:00 am EST on February 2nd, 2025. -From 9:00 pm EST February 2nd, 2025 until 9:00 am EST on February 3rd, 2025. <br/><br/><strong>• Get an Extra 15% or 20% off on SALE:</strong> applies only to purchases in our US online store (www.aguabendita.com). Buy 3 items from the “Sale” section and get an extra 15% off. Buy 4 or more items from the “Sale” section and get an extra 20% off. The discount will be automatically applied at the checkout. This promotion is valid from 4:00 am EST on January 30, 2025, to 7:00 am EST on January 31st, 2025.<br/><br/><strong>• Get an Extra 10% off on SALE:</strong> applies only to purchases in our US online store (www.aguabendita.com). Apply the code EXTRA10 at the checkout and get an extra 10% off on the “Sale” section. If the customer does not apply the code at the checkout, the discount will not be recognized after the order is placed. This promotion is valid only during the following time frames: -From 9:00 pm EST January 24th, 2025 until 9:00 am EST on January 25th, 2025. -From 9:00 pm EST January 25th, 2025 until 9:00 am EST on January 26th, 2025. -From 9:00 pm EST January 26th, 2025 until 9:00 am EST on January 27th, 2025. <br/> • January 1 to 31, 2025: enjoy an exclusive 25% birthday discount for customers registered in the Agua Bendita database. Valid only during your birthday month with prior registration. To redeem, enter the code sent in the birthday email at the USA Online Store: https://aguabendita.com/collections/new. This offer cannot be combined with other discounts or promotions and is not redeemable for cash. It does not apply to special collaborations and/or limited launches. For online redemption, customers must enter the code “E26BIRTHDAY01” at checkout. Valid for one (1) redemption during the birthday month. Promotional items are non-exchangeable, except in cases of warranty. For exchanges to a different item, the discount will not be retained; only the amount paid by the customer will be recognized. If the new item is of a lower value, the customer must add another item to complete the original amount or pay the difference if applicable.  <br/><br/>• AGUA BENDITA LLC. offers the promotional incentive called “35% DISCOUNT FOR SELECTED CUSTOMERS.” This promotion will be valid from 12:00 a.m. on January 1, 2026, until 11:59 p.m. on January 31, 2026. A 35% discount will be granted exclusively to selected customers who receive direct communication from the brand. The promotion applies to purchases made through Agua Bendita’s online store: https://www.aguabendita.com/collections/new. For online redemption, customers will need to enter the code they received via email or text message at the time of checkout. The discount is non-transferable, not redeemable for cash, and must be used in a single purchase. It is valid for one (1) redemption only and will be linked to the selected customer’s email address and identification document.To redeem the discount, the customer must enter the coupon code at checkout, which will be provided in the email communication. The discount cannot be combined with other discounts, promotions, special collections, or collaborations with other brands.All costs associated with the purchase, including shipping, taxes, deductions, and withholdings, will be covered by the customer and displayed at checkout. In the event of exchanges or warranty claims, the amount actually paid plus the 35% discount will be recognized. The discount will be valid for one (1) exchange only, and its value will be maintained even after the promotional period ends.This coupon is not valid on the international or Colombia websites. <br/><br/>• AGUA BENDITA LLC. makes available the promotional activity called “Additional 15%.” This promotion applies in physical stores and the USA online store, on selected items from the SALE category: https://www.aguabendita.com/collections/sale The benefit ranges from 30% to 60% off. The promotion will be valid from December 26, 2025, through January 1, 2026. During the event days, an additional 10% discount will be applied to the existing SALE discounts; that is, items discounted at 30% will become 40% off, 40% will become 50% off, and so on, up to the highest discount percentage. ONLINE STORE: Product availability will be indicated during size selection and once the item is added to the shopping cart. Any costs associated with the purchase, such as shipping, taxes, duties, withholdings, or similar charges, will be covered by the customer and will be displayed at checkout. PHYSICAL STORES: Participating items will be grouped accordingly, and availability will be subject to each store’s inventory. The discount will be reflected at the time of payment, once the cashier processes the invoice. This incentive cannot be combined with other discounts or promotions. In the case of exchanges or warranty claims, the value recognized will be the actual amount paid for the item. If an exchange is made for a different item after the promotion period has ended, the discount will not be honored. If the new item is of lower value, the customer must add another item to complete the remaining balance and/or pay any applicable difference. No refunds will be issued. No cash refunds will be issued. Final sale items are non-returnable and non-exchangeable, as stated in our return policy (https://www.aguabendita.com/pages/shipping-and-returns)</p>",
