                      "text": "",
                      "raw_text": "<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0598/7831/0042/files/Landing-Treasure-Hunter-Resort-2026-Logo.png?v=1754318439\" class=\"summer-collection-logo\" style=\"max-width: 280px; margin: 0 auto;\"><br>\n\n<p style=\"color:#000; \npadding: 0px 5px 15px;\nwidth: 500px;\n\">A Collector of Stories\n<br><br>\nShe’s a woman who journeys across Colombia in search of rare treasures—not just to adorn her body, but to carry pieces of this vibrant country with her.\n<br><br>\nIn hidden alleys and bustling markets, she uncovers objects that transform her: spices in a thousand colors, a silver necklace, a rug woven with centuries of history. Her style is a fusion of cultures, a continuous adventure where the true treasures aren’t the objects themselves, but the experiences and stories she gathers along the way. </p>",
